text: Mohand Chérif Hannachi (2 April 1950 – 13 November 2020) was an Algerian footballer. He was the chairman of JS Kabylie from 1993 until his death. Hannachi died on 13 November 2020 in Algiers at the age of 70. ==Honours== ===As Player=== ;JS Kabylie *Algerian League: 1973, 1974, 1977, 1980, 1982, 1983 *Algerian Cup: 1977 *African Cup of Champions Clubs: 1981 *CAF Super Cup: 1982 ===As Club President=== ;JS Kabylie *African Cup Winners Cup: 1995 *CAF Cup: 2000, 2001 and 2002 *Algerian League: 1995, 2004, 2006, 2008 *Algerian Cup: 1994, 2011 ==References== Category:1950 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Algerian footballers
title: Mohand Chérif Hannachi
